    <div class="calculator-box" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 10px; text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <h2>üöÄ Get Your FREE Medical Practice Valuation Now!</h2>
        <p>Calculate your medical practice worth in under 5 minutes using our proven SDE methodology.</p>
        <a href="https://thevaluationgenie.com/" class="cta-button">Calculate My Medical Practice Value</a>
        <p style="font-size: 0.9em; margin-top: 15px; opacity: 0.9;">Free estimate ‚Ä¢ Professional $39 reports available</p>
    </div>

    <article>
        <section id="introduction">
            <h2>Introduction to Medical Practice Valuation</h2>
            <p>Medical practice valuation is a specialized field that requires deep understanding of healthcare economics, regulatory requirements, and industry-specific metrics. In 2025, the healthcare landscape continues evolving with new technologies, changing reimbursement models, and increasing consolidation trends.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="sde-analysis">
            <h2>SDE Analysis for Medical Practices</h2>
            <p>Seller's Discretionary Earnings (SDE) is the most accurate method for <strong>medical practice valuation</strong>. Unlike traditional businesses, medical practices have unique financial structures that require specialized analysis.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="faq">
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
